---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import FileDropzone from '../components/upload/FileDropzone.svelte';
---

<Layout title="홈">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-8 py-12">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">🍒 CherryPicker</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
        카드 명세서를 업로드하면 카테고리별 최적 카드를 추천해 드립니다
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full max-w-2xl">
      <FileDropzone client:load />
    </div>

    <div class="grid w-full max-w-4xl grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-8">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface)] p-6 text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl">📊</div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 font-semibold">지출 분석</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
          CSV, Excel, PDF 명세서를 자동으로 인식하고 카테고리별로 분류합니다
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface)] p-6 text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl">🏆</div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 font-semibold">최적 카드 추천</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
          전월실적, 할인한도를 고려하여 카테고리별 최적 카드를 찾아줍니다
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface)] p-6 text-center">
        <div class="text-3xl">💰</div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 font-semibold">절약 시뮬레이션</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
          체리피킹 전후 혜택을 비교하고 연간 절약 금액을 확인하세요
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
